ADR-017: Agent-published apps. Agents call publish_app MCP tool to deploy web apps into containers. Apps show in sidebar under Apps, rendered via iframe at /apps/{name}/. Each app has a chat button that opens a conversation with the creating agent for iteration. Built-in Dashboard is the default app. Apps have versioning and rollback. Key design: app container is separate from agent container, proxied through xpressclaw server to avoid CORS.
